					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="Throwback Thursday: 8 Billionaire's First Tweets" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160627172209-warren-buffet.jpeg" rel="share" />

